<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Credits from Advanced Placement courses in which at least a 3 has been earned on the final examination are accepted by Waldorf College. A maximum of 3 courses will be accepted. Written departmental approval is required fo apply AP credit to major or minor.</i>
